            <lg xml:id="TK627">
<l>ilakka muṭampiṭumpaikkeṉṟu kalakkattaik </l>
<l> kaiyāṟāk koḷḷātā mēl</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great will not regard trouble as trouble, knowing that the body is the butt of trouble.</l>
